slist.%20Soon%2C%20my%20friend%20David%20and%20I%20were%20meeting%20customers%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpanera-founder-workers-not-motivated-making-money-shareholders-ceo-therapy-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPanera%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20lunch%20breaks%20to%20do%20on-the-spot%20repairs.%20That%20eventually%20led%20to%20our%20first%20uBreakiFix%20store%20opening%20in%20August%202009.%20The%20store%20outpaced%20our%20entire%20website's%20sales%2C%20and%20that%20success%20told%20us%20something%3A%20People%20didn't%20want%20to%20wait%20to%20mail%20out%20their%20devices.%20They%20needed%20fast%2C%20local%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20we%20grew%20to%2047%20corporate-owned%20locations.%20We%20franchised%20in%202012%20and%20eventually%20scaled%20to%20about%20550%20stores%20by%20the%20time%20I%20stepped%20away%20in%202021.%20We%20were%20the%20authorized%20repair%20partner%20for%20Google%20and%20Samsung%2C%20had%20contracts%20with%20top%20carriers%20and%20insurers%2C%20and%20built%20proprietary%20tech%20to%20ensure%20consistency%20and%20efficiency%20across%20our%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20stepping%20back%2C%20I%20took%20time%20to%20reset%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0spent%20more%20time%20with%20my%20family%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20thought%20about%20what%20was%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232991cc6-d1d5-450b-a61d-93df6faf732a%5C%22%3EThe%20bagel%20pivot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20next%20step%20came%20unexpectedly.%20A%20guy%20in%20our%20office%20started%20bringing%20in%20bagels%20on%20Fridays%2C%20and%20we%20were%20all%20blown%20away%20by%20the%20quality.%20The%20bagels%20were%20from%20Jeff's%20Bagel%20Run%2C%20a%20small%20operation%20in%20Florida%20started%20by%20Jeff%20and%20Danielle%20Perera%2C%20who%20had%20grown%20from%20baking%20at%20home%20to%20selling%20at%20farmers%20markets%20and%20eventually%20opening%20a%20couple%20of%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20intrigued%20%E2%80%94