ld%20executive%20coach%20based%20in%20Tennessee%2C%20who%20regularly%20travels%20internationally%2C%20and%20constantly%20works%20with%20frequent%20fliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20an%20involved%20routine%20of%20fasting%20on%20the%20plane%20and%20exercising%20on%20arrival%20to%20fend%20off%20jeg%20lag%20symptoms.%20But%20his%20biggest%20recommendation%20is%20to%20prevent%20jet%20lag%20in%20the%20first%20place%20by%20getting%20acclimated%20to%20a%20new%20time%20zone%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224626%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20artsy%20portrait%20photo%20of%20a%20man%20looking%20into%20the%20camera%20next%20to%20a%20window%20with%20dramatic%20lighting%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687922d8f748d8c055f5ce06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223469%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulian%20Hayes%20II%20is%20an%20executive%20coach%20who%20works%20with%20jet%20setters%2C%20and%20has%20his%20own%20carefully%20planned%20routine%20to%20manage%20air%20travel.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Julian%20Hayes%20II%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20before%20a%20flight%2C%20he%20shifts%20his%20sleeping%20schedule%20about%2030%20minutes%20at%20a%20time%20to%20more%20closely%20align%20to%20where%20he's%20traveling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20good%20rule%20is%20that%20it%20takes%20about%20one%20day%20per%20time%20zone%20you're%20crossing%20to%20get%20acclimated.%20A%20trip%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Europe%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20might%20take%20you%20about%20six%20days%20to%20recover%20from%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d4d19db-309f-47d7-8b6f-ad1fca0fc9af%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20pro%20athlete%20swears%20by%20the%20'NBA%20nap'%20and%20basic%20supplements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freduce-inflammation-pro-athlete-easy-diet-exercise-tips-nba-allstar-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENBA%20star%20Kevin%20Love%3C%2Fa%