ve%20a%20great%20cleaning%20crew%20and%20you%20have%20all%20of%20your%20messaging%20locked%20in%20and%20your%20check-in%20instructions%2C%20it's%20pretty%20much%20automated%20and%20doesn't%20require%20much%20of%20our%20time%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2266f7bad8-894d-401e-856c-8d4aecf59eca%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20PriceLabs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhello.pricelabs.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPriceLabs%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20tool%20that%20helps%20you%20accurately%20price%20your%20rental%20units%20based%20on%20demand%20and%20seasonality%20in%20your%20area.%20Manny%20Reyna%2C%20who%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-retired-early-in-japan-buying-rental-properties-real-estate-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elives%20with%20his%20family%20in%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20but%20owns%20rentals%20in%20Texas%2C%20uses%20it%20to%20manage%20his%20portfolio%20from%20abroad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt%20automates%20the%20pricing%20for%20you%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20into%20the%20apps%20and%20keep%20updating%20the%20prices%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20meant%20to%20increase%20booking%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Reyna.%20%26quot%3BSay%20there's%20some%20special%20event%20going%20on.%20It'll%20raise%20the%20prices%20for%20you%20to%20meet%20that%20demand.%20Or%2C%20if%20nothing's%20really%20going%20on%20in%20the%20area%2C%20it'll%20lower%20the%20prices%20for%20you%20so%20that%20your%20listing%20stays%20competitive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tool%20does%20more%20than%20recommend%20prices.%20It%20has%20a%20market%20dashboard%20that%20helps%20you%20analyze%20markets%20for%20investment%20potential.%20It's%20how%20San%20Diego-based%20real%20estate%20investor%20Kent%20He%20chose%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-succeed-make-money-on-airbnb-short-term-rentals-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20short-term%20rentals%20in%20Scottsdale%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20even%20helped%20him%20select%20the%20specific%20neighborhood%20in%20the%20desert%20city.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20used%20PriceLabs%20to%20look%20at%20the%20top%20200%20listings%20in%20Scottsdale.%20Then%2C%20he%20did%20a%20keyword%20search%20in%20the%20reviews%20section%20of%20each%20listing.%20Specifically%2C%20he%20was%20looking%20for%20how%20many%20times%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Blocation%26quot%3B%20popped%20up%20in%20the%20reviews.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20generally%20a%20positive%20connotation%20associated%20with%20that%20word%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%2C%20so%20he%20was%20looking%20for%20properties%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20mentions%20of%20%26quot%3Blocation%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20reviews.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20you%20know%20which%20neighborhoods%20people%20are%20raving%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d14b778f-2afa-4d08-9081-391a4351e548%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Rankbreeze%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20tool%20He%20likes%20to%20use%20is%20a%20listing%20optimization%20software%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frankbreeze.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERankbreeze%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20helps%20hosts%20fine-tune%20the%20description%20of%20their%20property%20and%20discover%20amenities%20that%20guests%20in%20their%20area%20are%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20his%20favorite%20features%20is%20the%20A%2FB%20testing%2C%20which%20lets%20you%20change%20your%20cover%20photo%20or%20pet%20policy%2C%20for%20example%2C%20to%20see%20how%20it%20affects%20your%20Airbnb%20ranking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221086%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kent%20he%20family%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64836eb4323ab800198555f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAirbnb%20host%20Kent%20He%20and%20his%20family.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kent%20He%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BOn%20Google%2C%20no%20one%20really%20goes%20to%20page%20five%20or%2010%20after%20searching.%20It's%20the%20same%20for%20Airbnb.%20You%20want%20to%20be%20ranked%20as%20high%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BI%20use%20Rankbreeze%20to%20play%20around%20with%20my%20cover%20photos%20to%20see%20which%20one%20allows%20me%20to%20rank%20highest.%20I%20also%20play%20around%20with%20the%20listing%20title.%20For%20example%2C%20during%20colder%20months%2C%20I%20might%20highlight%20that%20we%20have%20a%20heated%20pool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20could%20offer%20the%20best%20Airbnb%20property%20in%20your%20area%2C%20but%20if%20it's%20not%20properly%20marketed%2C%20guests%20may%20never%20see%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEspecially%20with%20the%20cover%20photo%2C%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20waste%20that%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20He.%20%26quot%3BBe%20intentional%20with%20your%20listing%20title%20and%20call%20out%20to%20your%20target%20customer%20so%20that%20they're%20more%20likely%20to%20click.%20Because%20if%20they%20never%20click%20into%20your%20listing%2C%20they'll%20never%20book%20with%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-tools-to-grow-your-airbnb-short-term-rental-business-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752830102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687877f185e81483682e2a66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-tools-to-grow-your-airbnb-short-term-rental-business-2025-7%2