anically%26quot%3B%20come%20in%20five%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Fridays%2C%20employees%20at%20Sendbird's%20headquarters%20are%20treated%20to%20a%20free%20lunch%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20perks%20of%20showing%20up%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeji%20Yoon%2C%20the%20company's%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company's%20chief%20financial%20officer%20started%20the%20office%20tradition%20for%20%26quot%3Bselfish%26quot%3B%20reasons%3A%20He%20loves%20bahn%20mi%20sandwiches%2C%20particularly%20those%20from%20a%20local%20Vietnamese%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFridays%20aren't%20official%20in-person%20days.%20Since%20early%202024%2C%20the%20company%20has%20required%20those%20who%20can%20come%20into%20its%20San%20Mateo%20headquarters%20to%20be%20on-site%20Monday%2C%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20Thursday.%20It's%20also%20rolling%20out%20return-to-office%20mandates%20at%20its%20other%20offices%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20a%20few%20of%20the%20company's%20teams%2C%20including%20the%20finance%20team%2C%20decided%20to%20come%20on%20Fridays%2C%20too%2C%20because%20it%20was%20easier%20to%20collaborate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20CFO%20would%20start%20going%20around%20asking%20anyone%20else%20in%20the%20office%2C%20do%20you%20want%20a%20sandwich%3F%26quot%3B%20Yoon%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20became%20this%20regular%20thing%2C%20so%20it%20grew%20extremely%20organically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20there's%20a%20Slack%20channel%20dedicated%20to%20Friday%20office%20lunch.%20Bahn%20mi%20orders%20are%20entered%20onto%20a%20Google%20Sheet%2C%20and%20everyone%20who%20participates%20has%20to%20submit%20their%20orders%20by%2011%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20%26quot%3Bfun%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20performance%20marketing%20managers%20started%20looking%20at%20the%20data%3A%20total%20orders%20over%20time%2C%20the%20most%20popular%20customization%20%E2%80%94%20no%20peppers%2C%20more%20cilantro%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20orders%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20number%20of%20people%20on%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conclusion%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Bfood%20is%20definitely%20a%20way%20to%20keep%20people%20or%20bring%20people%20in%20the%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20Yoon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20academics%2C%20sociologists%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmother-return-to-the-office-commute-childcare-nightmare-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworking%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20all%20lauded%20the%20benefits%20of%20remote%20work%2C%20Yoon%20said%20it's%20just%20not%20practical%20anymore%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20new%20changes%20in%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemote%20roles%20are%20best%20when%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20no%20real%20dependency%20on%20collaboration%20or%20iterations%20or%20real-time%20decision-making%20that%20needs%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20especially%20with%20AI%2C%20where%20everything%20is%20changing%20so%20quickly%2C%20product%20is%20changing%20so%20quickly%2C%20customers'%20expectations%20are%20changing%20really%20quickly%20%E2%80%94%20nobody%20really%20knows%20how%20fast%20everything%20is%20changing.%20They%20don't%20really%20understand%20it.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20collaboration%20that%20has%20to%20happen%20on%20the%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20of%20work%20and%20the%20company's%20product%20releases%20slow%20down%20when%20workers%20are%20remote%2C%20she%20said.%20And%20while%20there%20are%20no%20plans%20to%20force%20employees%20to%20come%20into%20the%20office%20on%20Fridays%2C%20the%20free%20bahm%20mi%20might%20be%20all%20they%20need%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffree-lunch-office-rto-return-to-office-jobs-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752827461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3