.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fhome-garden-1-1752771702-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fhome-garden-1-1752771702-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fhome-garden-1-1752771702-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fhome-garden-1-1752771702-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471763%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20women%20of%20Jharkhand%20have%20become%20an%20active%20part%20in%20the%20decision-making%20process%20regarding%20the%20solar%20microgrids%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20take%20these%20meetings%20seriously.%20As%20Suchita%20Ba%2C%20who%20heads%20them%20in%20her%20village%20in%20Kudpani%20Girijatoli%2C%20Simdega%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20these%20meetings%2C%20we%20collect%20the%20monthly%20tariff%20of%20Rs%20100%20from%20each%20family.%20Initially%2C%20every%20family%20pooled%20in%20Rs%202%2C000.%20The%20money%20is%20a%20backup%3B%20if%20the%20microgrids%20need%20maintenance%2C%20we%20can%20pay%20for%20it%20ourselves.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuchita%20is%20a%20busy%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F418417%2Ftanveer-inamdar-treei-foundation-portable-solar-energy-solution-tribal-families%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earrival%20of%20%E2%80%98light%E2%80%99%20in%20her%20village%3C%2Fa%3E%20gave%20her%20a%20lot%20to%20do%2C%20such%20as%20making%20decisions%20on%20how%20it%E2%80%99s%20used.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20have%20electricity%20for%20years.%20And%20then%20one%20day%2C%20we%20did.%20Now%20our%20lives%20look%20very%20different.%20My%20children%20can%20study.%20It%20gave%20us%20access%20to%20so%20many%20more%20facilities.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20freedom%20came%20with%20responsibility.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20put%20our%20own%20money%2C%20we%20feel%20responsible%20for%20the%20microgrids.%20Another%20reason%20why%20we%20do%20this%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20grids%20help%20our%20children%2C%20too.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20also%20benefit%20from%20solar.%20We%20are%20saving%20for%20our%20future.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacked%20by%20Gram%20Oorja%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Gumla%20are%20turning%20into%20custodians%20of%20their%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20success%20of%20the%20model%2C%20Sameer%2C%20one%20of%20the%20founders%20of%20Gram%20Oorja%2C%20says%20it%E2%80%99s%20hinged%20on%20two%20key%20players%20%E2%80%94%20CSR%20grants%20(which%20help%20with%20capital%20costs)%20and%20tariffs%2C%20which%20cover%20the%20maintenance%20costs.%20The%20latter%20is%20as%20crucial%20as%20the%20former%20because%20they%20allow%20for%20a%20judicious%20use%20of%20the%20resources.%20This%20is%20important%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20as%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268152%2Fmaharashtra-village-manyachiwadi-solar-gram-electricity-sustainable-women-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocals%20witness%20continuous%20power%20supply%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20tendency%20to%20view%20it%20as%20a%20rare%20indulgence.%20Tariffs%20ensure%20prudent%20use.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20them%20a%20part%20of%20the%20process%20ensures%20that%20the%20model%20goes%20beyond%20a%20fleeting%20inclusion%20and%20instead%20sustains%20itself%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20Over%20the%20life%20cycle%20of%20the%20project%2C%20the%20village%20bears%20around%2060%20percent%20of%20the%20overall%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gumla%2C%20a%20constant%20power%20supply%20guarantees%20more%20than%20just%20peace%20of%2