'%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20said%20during%20Netflix's%20first%20quarter%20earnings%20call%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20remains%20a%20thorny%20issue%20in%20society%20writ%20large%20and%20in%20Hollywood%20in%20particular.%20Demands%20over%20AI%20usage%20were%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20historic%20dual%20actors%20and%20writers'%20strikes%20that%20shut%20down%20production%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFans%20expressed%20frustration%20at%20Disney%20in%202023%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecret-invasion-marvel-series-ai-intro-sequence-fans-furious-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMarvel%20Studios'%20choice%20to%20use%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20credit%20art%20in%20%26quot%3BSecret%20Invasion%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Disney%2B%20series.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftyler-perry-ai-studio-productions-movies-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETyler%20Perry%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20said%20he%20has%20paused%20studio%20expansion%20plans%20because%20of%20the%20AI%20capabilities%20that%20are%20already%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisual%20effects%20is%20one%20area%20of%20Hollywood%20that%20could%20be%20drastically%20changed%20by%20AI%2C%20as%20audiences%20demand%20explosive%20climaxes%20and%20superhero%20features%20that%20strain%20production%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Netflix's%20news%20illustrates%2C%20it%20won't%20just%20be%20summer%20blockbusters%20that%20are%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-generative-ai-use-artificial-intelligence-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752821221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68797b743d5881a51c1d9036%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-generative-ai-use-artificial-intelligence-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%20revealed%