053%2Fsustainable-nainital-homestay-bir-terraces-recycles-greywater-rainfall-harvesting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etomatoes%2C%20and%20plums%3C%2Fa%3E%20spoil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20no%20electricity%20to%20run%20dryers%20or%20refrigerators.%20Watching%20all%20that%20produce%20rot%20was%20heartbreaking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20For%20Verazo%20and%20many%20like%20him%2C%20the%20emotional%20toll%20was%20only%20part%20of%20the%20loss.%20The%20financial%20damage%20from%20spoiled%20produce%20cut%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20nearby%20Dzulhami%20village%2C%2074-year-old%20Nepruzu%20Keyho%20recalls%20his%20own%20struggle.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20dry%20turmeric%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20medicinal%20plants%20under%20the%20sun.%20But%20rain%20or%20insects%20would%20ruin%20everything.%20It%20was%20a%20long%2C%20tiring%20process%20that%20often%20ended%20in%20disappointment.%E2%80%9D%20Their%20stories%20reflect%20a%20larger%20reality%20%E2%80%94%20traditional%20methods%20of%20drying%20and%20storing%20harvests%20are%20failing%2C%20especially%20in%20villages%20without%20steady%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20parts%20of%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20hilly%20terrain%2C%20poor%20infrastructure%20leaves%20farmers%20with%20few%20options.%20Crops%20are%20grown%20with%20care%2C%20only%20to%20decay%20before%20they%20can%20be%20sold.%20But%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Porba%2C%20a%20gentle%20shift%20is%20underway.%20One%20young%20man%20is%20helping%20change%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20just%2026%2C%20Swuyievezo%20Dzudo%20has%20built%20a%20low-cost%20solar%20dryer%20%E2%80%94%20a%20simple%2C%20electricity-free%20device%20that%E2%80%99s%20helping%20farmers%20preserve%20their%20produce%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328356%2Fhyderabad-recykal-marketplace-sell-waste-online-empower-scrap-dealers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20waste%2C%20and%20earn%2