0solar%20dryer%20offers%20a%20much-needed%20alternative%3A%20affordable%2C%20customisable%2C%20and%20built%20from%20materials%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20strain%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20pocket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-foot%20model%20costs%20approximately%20Rs%207%2C000%2C%20while%20larger%20units%20measuring%2010%20by%2010%20feet%20range%20between%20Rs%2025%2C000%20and%20Rs%2030%2C000.%20The%20lower%20cost%20is%20possible%20because%20of%20the%20use%20of%20readily%20available%20materials%20such%20as%20bamboo%2C%20wood%2C%20aluminium%20cans%2C%20UV%20sheets%2C%20and%20solar%20panels%20%E2%80%94%20all%20chosen%20to%20reduce%20expenses%20without%20compromising%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291233%2Fkerala-man-uses-steel-builds-eco-friendly-low-cost-home-thats-earthquake-fire-resistant%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%20is%20low%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20far%20we%20have%20been%20providing%20the%20solar%20dryers%20free%20of%20charge%20to%20farmers%20in%20five%20villages%20of%20Nagaland%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20every%20farmer%2C%20regardless%20of%20income%2C%20can%20access%20this%20technology%20and%20improve%20their%20livelihoods.%E2%80%9D%20The%20five%20beneficiary%20villages%20%E2%80%94%20Porba%2C%20Thuvopisu%2C%20Dzulhami%2C%20Runguzu%2C%20and%20Ciepoketa%20%E2%80%94%20have%20seen%20about%20500%20farmers%20receive%20these%20dryers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20on%20local%20farmers%20has%20been%20powerful%20and%20immediate.%20Verazo%2C%20who%20constructed%20two%20solar%20dryers%20on%20his%20farm%20with%20Swuyievezo%E2%80%99s%20guidance%2C%20explains%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20quality%20of%20dried%20kiwi%20and%20other%20fruits%20is%20excellent.%20The%20dryer%20preserves%20the%20flavour%20and%20colour%2C%20and%20the%20shelf%20life%20i