%20saffron%20bulbs%20for%20Rs%20eight%20lakh%20from%20Pampore.%20%E2%80%9COf%20this%2C%20we%20could%20use%20700%20kg%20that%20met%20the%20criteria%20for%20cultivation.%20It%20is%20advised%20to%20grow%20saffron%20bulbs%20weighing%20seven%20grams%3B%20otherwise%2C%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20result%20in%20flowering.%20We%20nurtured%20the%20remaining%20bulbs%20for%20the%20next%20cycle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20detail%20of%20Anil%E2%80%99s%20indoor%20farm%20is%20tailored%20to%20replicate%20the%20conditions%20of%20a%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20field.%20From%20regulating%20temperatures%20between%20eight%20to%2025%20degrees%20Celsius%20to%20maintaining%20humidity%20levels%2C%20every%20parameter%20was%20fine-tuned%20to%20perfection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20saffron%20bloomed%2C%20Anil%20says%2C%20stringent%20hygiene%20practices%20were%20implemented%2C%20akin%20to%20intensive%20care%20cleanliness%20standards.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wash%20our%20hands%20with%2070%20percent%20Isopropyl%20Alcohol%20(IPA)%20solution%20(a%20disinfectant)%20and%20we%20wear%20hand%20gloves%20and%20protective%20gear%20before%20entering%20the%20indoor%20farm.%20This%20prevents%20any%20possible%20contamination%20or%20fungal%20growth%20in%20saffron%20bulbs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20meticulously%20regulates%20carbon%20dioxide%20levels%2C%20light%20exposure%2C%20and%20bulb%20hygiene%20to%20ensure%20a%20thriving%20crop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20November%2C%20his%20efforts%20bore%20fruit%2C%20as%20he%20proudly%20harvested%201%2C600%20grams%20of%20saffron.%20Following%20the%20harvest%2C%20he%20dried%20the%20delicate%20red%20stigmas%20and%20ensured%20their%20safe%20storage%20to%20prevent%20fungal%20growth.%20Selling%20it%20at%20Rs%20500%20per%20gram%2C%20Anil%20reaped%20a%20substantial%20Rs%20eight%20lakh%20from%20his%20first%20yield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fsaffron-1-1752578265.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20also%20enhances%20their%20homemade%20sweets%20with%20homegrown%20authentic%20saffron.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fsaffron-1-1752578265.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fsaffron-1-1752578265-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fsaffron-1-1752578265-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fsaffron-1-1752578265-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fsaffron-1-1752578265-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-470367%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20also%20enhances%20their%20homemade%20sweets%20with%20homegrown%20authentic%20saffron.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBrought%20the%20farm%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20shares%20that%20his%20wife%2C%20Kalpana%20Jaiswal%2C%20is%20integral%20to%20their%20daily%20operations%2C%20particularly%20excelling%20in%20meticulous%20attention%20to%20detail.%20As%20part%20of%20their%20commitment%2C%20they%20recreate%20the%20natural%20habitat%20of%20saffron%20with%20utmost%20precision%2C%20even%20incorporating%20the%20soothing%20bird%20songs%20reminiscent%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20landscapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalpana%20orchestrated%20operations%20with%20seamless%20precision%2C%20from%20nurturing%20bulbs%20to%20the%20precise%20timing%20of%20temperature%2C%20watering%2C%20and%20their%20timely%20harvest.%20Sharing%20her%20experience%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20visited%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20saffron%2