hem%20in%20a%20more%20fun%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20is%20it%20working%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spring%20in%20Smita%E2%80%99s%20step%20and%20the%20decibel%20of%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20responses%20suggest%20it%20is.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20used%20to%20teach%20concepts%20in%20the%20usual%20ways.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F303196%2Famazon-future-engineer-programme-helps-underprivileged-children-learn-robotics-coding-ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOur%20classrooms%20have%20changed%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20our%20school%20collaborated%20with%20the%20Language%20and%20Learning%20Foundation.%20Our%20walls%20are%20now%20filled%20with%20stories%2C%20and%20children%20want%20to%20learn.%20They%20feel%20enthusiastic%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20workbook%20does%20not%20just%20focus%20on%20questions%20but%20also%20on%20activities.%20I%20teach%20Hindi%20and%20math%3B%20in%20Hindi%2C%20we%20usually%20solve%20the%20vocabulary%20that%20is%20given%20in%20the%20textbooks.%20But%20with%20the%20workbooks%2C%20children%20learn%20how%20to%20identify%20the%20alphabet%20and%20how%20to%20use%20it%20in%20their%20daily%20language.%20The%20books%20give%20us%20different%20ways%20of%20teaching%20them%20poems%20and%20stories.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStories%20like%20these%20thrill%20Jhingran.%20It%E2%80%99s%20antithetical%20to%20the%20reality%20that%20he%20watched%20unfolding%20in%20the%20classrooms%20of%20Kokrajhar%20during%20his%20posting%20there.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20find%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F84823%2Fhow-reduce-illiteracy-rates-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20sitting%20passively%20in%20classrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20teacher%20would%20be%20doing%20the%20speaking%3B%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20the%20children%20were%20often%20even%20understanding%20what%20was%20happening.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20probing%20and%20conversations%20with%20the%20students%20revealed%20there%20was%20a%20language%20barrier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20children%20were%20used%20to%20speaking%20one%20language%20at%20home%20and%20were%20being%20taught%20in%20a%20different%20language%20in%20school.%20There%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jhingran%20adds%20that%20the%20paucity%20of%20educational%20facilities%2C%20compounded%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20most%20children%20only%20spoke%20the%20tribal%20dialect%2C%20was%20slow-rippling%20into%20illiteracy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dhir%20Jhingran%20is%20attempting%20to%20bridge%20the%20gaps%20that%20exist%20in%20foundational%20literacy%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-469649%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDhir%20Jhingran%20is%20attempting%20to%20bridge%20the%20gaps%20that%20exist%20in%20foundational%20literacy%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20extrapolated%20this%20to%20other%20tribal%20belts%20and%20remote%20areas%20of%20India%2C%20he%20found%20the%20situation%20there%20too%20mirrored%20Kokrajhar%E2%80%99s%20reality.%20There%20was%20a%20fast%20widening%20educational%20chasm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJhingran%20devised%20a%20three-step%20approach%20to%20tackle%20the%20problem.%20At%20the%20Language%20and%20Learning%20Foundation%2C%20these%20pathways%2C%20as%20Jhingran%20calls%20them%2C%20converge%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F458364%2Fmitti-ka-ghar-in-bhopal-by-muskaan-ngo-sustainable-architecture-to-help-denotified-tribes-pardhi-and-gondi-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraising%20a%20generation%20of%20students%20who%20can%20read%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20write%2C%20and%20think.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20more%20about%20the%20three%20approaches%2C%20he%20says%20the%20first%20is%20a%20continuous%20string%20of%20in-person%20workshops%2C%20online%20courses%2C%20and%20cluster%20meetings%20that%20bolster%20teachers%E2%80%99%20confidence%3B%20then%20follows%20collaborations%20with%20government%20agencies%20to%20help%20mainstream%20best%20practices%20%E2%80%94%20MoUs%20have%20been%20signed%20with%20state%20governments%20of%20Assam%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Thirdly%2C%20teachers%20are%20equipped%20with%20workbooks%2C%20guides%2C%20handbooks%2C%20and%20targeted%20daily%20lesson%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20interactive%20teaching%20approaches%2C%20workbooks%20and%20discussions%20students%20are%20taught%20concepts%20that%20they%20may%20have%20otherwise%20found%20difficult%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-469655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThrough%20interactive%20teaching%20approaches%2C%20workbooks%2C%20and%20discussions%2C%20students%20are%20taught%20concepts%20that%20may%20have%20been%20difficult.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20career%20is%20chequered.%20Jhingran%20has%20spent%20a%20decade%20working%20with%20the%20government%20of%20Assam%20to%20improve%20literacy%20programmes%3B%20worked%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Human%20Resource%20Development%2C%20during%20which%20he%20supervised%20and%20coordinated%20the%20District%20Primary%20Education%20Program%20(DPEP)%20in%20eight%20states%3B%20led%20the%20Government%20of%20India-United%20Nations%E2%80%99%20Joint%20Program%20for%20Primary%20Education%20in%20eight%20Indian%20states%3B%20was%20National%20Education%20Advisor%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Government%20of%20Nepal%20and%20was%20senior%20advisor%20(education)%2C%20UNICEF%2C%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20lack%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nore